This project requires:
SBT
Scala
Spark

To build:
sbt/sbt assembly

To run:
$SPARK_DIR/bin/spark-submit --class br.ufrgs.inf.Minimantics PATH/pdp/target/scala-2.10/Minimantics-assembly-0.0.1.jar iINPUT_FILE oOUTPUT_FILE S0.2 acond_prob

For example:
/opt/spark/bin/spark-submit --class br.ufrgs.inf.Minimantics /home/user/pdp/target/scala-2.10/Minimantics-assembly-0.0.1.jar ifile:///mini.1.s.filter.t10.c10.tc2.u ofile:///res S0.2 acond_prob
